Standard and Poor's Corp said itaffirmed the B-plus rating on AVX Corp's 28 mln dlrs ofsubordinated debt.    The company's implied senior debt rating is BB.    S and P said AVX's purchase offer for CTS Corp &lt;CTS> hasexpired and the acquisition does not appear likely to occur.AVX was listed on S and P's creditwatch with negativeimplications on December 17, 1986, because of the proposedacquisition. Reuter&#3;